{"title":"滤波电路设计","uid":"7654cddd589d5117806bb3f535f9e67b","slug":"滤波电路设计","date":"2023-11-07T15:33:17.000Z","updated":"2024-11-04T05:31:50.253Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/滤波电路设计.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/22/l3htjIV41UgP7kc.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><p>滤波电路是一种用于过滤信号的电路，它将仅传递所需的信号并滤去不需要的信号。通常，滤波电路由无源元件或有源元件设计。</p>\n<p>· 无源元件包括电阻器、电感器和电容器。</p>\n<p>· 有源元件包括BJT、MOSFET和运算放大器。</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><strong>低通滤波电路</strong>:一种允许频率低于一个确定频率阈值的信号通过，并且阻止高于该确定频率阈值的信号通过的电子电路。<br><strong>低通滤波电路</strong>允许低频信号通过，并抑制高频信号。其核心思想是在频率域上通过移除高频成分来平滑信号。这在去噪、平滑和提取基本频率成分时非常有用。</p>\n<p><strong>高通滤波电路</strong>:一种允许频率高于一个确定频率阈值的信号通过，并且阻止低于该确定频率阈值的信号通过的电子电路。<br><strong>高通滤波电路</strong>允许高频信号通过，并抑制低频信号。它的工作原理与低通滤波电路相反，通过移除低频成分来突出高频特征。</p>\n\n</details>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/11/08/wN6hHaWnMYryuOD.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-11-08 135542.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"无源高通滤波电路\"><a href=\"#无源高通滤波电路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"无源高通滤波电路\"></a>无源高通滤波电路</h2><p>仅由无源器件构成的<strong>通高频阻低频</strong>的滤波电路。</p>\n<p>最简单的无源高通滤波电路就是一个电阻+一个电容</p>\n<p>截止频率 <del>$f_L &#x3D; \\frac{1}{2πRC}$</del> <em>f &#x3D; 1&#x2F;(2πRC)</em>,高于 <del>$f_L$</del> <em>f</em>可通，低于<del>$f_L$</del> <em>f</em>衰减</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><p>此处的通高频阻低频都是<strong>相对的</strong>，本人习惯认为k量级以下的为低频，G量级以上的为高频。<strong>这不唯一</strong>，实际电路应根据实际需要的信号进行分析。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"无源低通滤波电路\"><a href=\"#无源低通滤波电路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"无源低通滤波电路\"></a>无源低通滤波电路</h2><p>仅由无源器件构成的<strong>通低频阻高频</strong>的滤波电路。</p>\n<p>最简单的无源低通滤波电路也就是一个电阻+一个电容</p>\n<p>截止频率 <del>$ f_L &#x3D; \\frac{1}{2πRC} $</del> <em>f &#x3D; 1&#x2F;(2πRC)</em> ，低于<del>$ f_L $</del> <em>f</em>可通，高于<del>$ f_L $</del> <em>f</em>衰减</p>\n<p>感兴趣的读者可以去Multisim上验证</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">WARNING</p>\n<p>无源滤波通常放大倍数及其截止频率随负载变化，在实际电路中负载会变化会导致无源滤波的参数改变而可能导致信号的失真。</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"有源低通滤波电路\"><a href=\"#有源低通滤波电路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"有源低通滤波电路\"></a>有源低通滤波电路</h2><p>由有源器件构成的<strong>通低频阻高频</strong>的滤波电路。</p>\n<p>介绍基础的有源一阶低通滤波电路</p>\n<p>在无源低通滤波电路中加入高输入阻抗，低输出阻抗的隔离电路（后级电路输入低阻抗）-&gt;电压跟随器</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p><p>高输入电抗可以保证原先无源低通滤波电路的参数的稳定，负载都趋于无穷了。。。<br>低输出电抗可以保证信号的纯净度，减小干扰。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<p>将无源滤波电路与运放组合<br>可以做到滤波+信号放大</p>\n<h2 id=\"有源高通滤波电路\"><a href=\"#有源高通滤波电路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"有源高通滤波电路\"></a>有源高通滤波电路</h2><p>由有源器件构成的<strong>通高频阻低频</strong>的滤波电路。</p>\n<h2 id=\"带通滤波电路\"><a href=\"#带通滤波电路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"带通滤波电路\"></a>带通滤波电路</h2><p>只保留某一段频率带，抑制或衰减其他频率带的滤波电路</p>\n<p>懂点电路原理知道了<strong>LRC电路</strong>就可以知道实际上这有个<strong>通频带</strong>的概念。</p>\n<h2 id=\"带阻滤波电路\"><a href=\"#带阻滤波电路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"带阻滤波电路\"></a>带阻滤波电路</h2><p>只抑制或衰减某一段频率带，对其他频率无影响的滤波电路，可以认为是与带通滤波电路互补的。</p>\n<h2 id=\"实际电路中的滤波电路分析\"><a href=\"#实际电路中的滤波电路分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实际电路中的滤波电路分析\"></a>实际电路中的滤波电路分析</h2><h3 id=\"电容的实际等效模型\"><a href=\"#电容的实际等效模型\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"电容的实际等效模型\"></a>电容的实际等效模型</h3><p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/11/08/OfB21QWUPm6piDr.png\" alt=\"屏幕截图 2023-11-08 141635.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">阻抗计算公式</p>\n<p>阻抗<br><del>$ Z &#x3D; ESR + jωL + &#x2F;frac{1}{jωC} $</del><br><em>Z &#x3D; ESR + jωL + 1&#x2F;jωC</em><br>其中<del>$ω &#x3D; 2πf$</del> <em>ω &#x3D; 2πf</em></p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/11/08/peOEb7Thi4Y38uf.png\" alt=\"b4186551b09d4a29bb4a70bf32b4452a.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">性质</p>\n<p>当 f &#x3D; <em>f</em> 时，<em>Z&#x3D;ESR</em>  此时电容相当于一个<strong>纯电阻</strong>， <em>f</em> 为其谐振频率<br>当 f &gt; <em>f</em> 时， 电容呈<strong>感性</strong>(像电感一样阻高频)<br>当 f &lt; <em>f</em> 时， 电容呈<strong>容性</strong>(像电容一样阻低频)</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">举例</p>\n<p>因此，当电容作高频滤波时，应工作在容性即f &lt; <em>f</em> 的条件下</p>\n<p>一般电容厂商会提供电容的数据手册上会有电容的阻抗-频率曲线，可以对应到谐振频率</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/11/08/u5m3OPgjrxcEoI4.gif\" alt=\"1718177965.gif\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"芯片电源引脚为什么加100nF电容？\"><a href=\"#芯片电源引脚为什么加100nF电容？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"芯片电源引脚为什么加100nF电容？\"></a>芯片电源引脚为什么加100nF电容？</h3><p>该电容常常称为<strong>旁路电容</strong></p>\n<p>该电容需要尽量靠近电源引脚，因为如果摆放很远的话，电容滤除噪声后的电源会在这个段路径上又串扰进新的噪声，那么这个电容的作用就没有太大的意义。。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">作用</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>滤除电源上的高频噪声</strong>–显然的</li>\n<li><strong>储能</strong>–芯片电源端进行供电时可以就近供能，减小电源平面干扰，不然拉长从电源平面易产生噪声（电压波动）</li>\n<li><strong>减小高频信号的回流路径</strong>–高频回路路径大会导致对其他器件的电磁干扰</li>\n</ol>\n\n</div>\n<p>常用数字芯片信号频率基本都在10MHz以下，电源上的干扰或其自身干扰大概100nF的谐振频率之下，因此电源引脚旁路电容经验值100nF。</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>Click to see more</summary>\n<p><p>芯片信号频率比较高可以选择小容值</p>\n<p>容值与频率的对应参考（懒人不想看数据手册）</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">频率范围</th>\n<th align=\"center\">推荐容值</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">DC-100KHz</td>\n<td align=\"center\">10uF</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">100KHz-10MHz</td>\n<td align=\"center\">100nF</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">10MHz-100MHz</td>\n<td align=\"center\">10nF</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">&gt;100M</td>\n<td align=\"center\">1nF</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p>可以去<strong>Multisim</strong>上进行电路仿真感受以下滤波的工作机理</p>\n</p>\n</details>\n","text":"前言滤波电路是一种用于过滤信号的电路，它将仅传递所需的信号并滤去不需要的信号。通常，滤波电路由无源元件或有源元件设计。 · 无源元件包括电阻器、电感器和电容器。...","permalink":"/post/滤波电路设计","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Electronic","slug":"Electronic","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Electronic.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"design","slug":"design","count":2,"path":"api/tags/design.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前言</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%97%A0%E6%BA%90%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9A%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">无源高通滤波电路</span></a></li><li class=\"toc